sections.markdown:
# Hands On 1
Running a query against the Web App to see all the insurance quotes that are going out to the customers

input.value:
fetch logs
| filter (azure.resource.group == "SCW-GROUP-HOTX1")
| filter (azure.resource.type == "MICROSOFT.WEB/SITES")
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson 
| parse contentjson.resultDescription, "DATA '] ' JSON:resultDescription"
| fieldsFlatten resultDescription 
| fieldsKeep timestamp, "resultDescription.*"
| sort timestamp, direction:"descending"
| limit 1000

fetch logs
| filter azure.resource.group == "SCW-GROUP-HOTX1"
| filter azure.resource.type == "MICROSOFT.WEB/SITES"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| parse contentjson.resultDescription, "DATA '] ' JSON:resultDescription"
| fieldsFlatten resultDescription
| fieldsKeep timestamp, "resultDescription.*"
| sort timestamp, direction:"descending"
| limit 1000

# Hands On 2 
Getting the records where the Web App is quoting $1 for Insurance

fetch logs
| filter (azure.resource.group == "SCW-GROUP-HOTX1")
| filter (azure.resource.type == "MICROSOFT.WEB/SITES")
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson 
| parse contentjson.resultDescription, "DATA '] ' JSON:resultDescription"
| fieldsFlatten resultDescription 
| fieldsKeep timestamp, resultDescription.PolicyEstimate, resultDescription.CustRef, resultDescription.PreviousInsurer, resultDescription.Messages
| filter resultDescription.PolicyEstimate == 1
| sort timestamp, direction:"descending"
| limit 1000

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch logs
| filter azure.resource.group == "SCW-GROUP-HOTX1"
| filter azure.resource.type == "MICROSOFT.WEB/SITES"
| parse content, "JSON:contentjson"
| fieldsFlatten contentjson
| parse contentjson.resultDescription, "DATA '] ' JSON:resultDescription"
| fieldsFlatten resultDescription
| fieldsKeep timestamp, resultDescription.PolicyEstimate, resultDescription.CustRef, resultDescription.PreviousInsurer, resultDescription.Messages
| filter resultDescription.PolicyEstimate == 1
| sort timestamp, direction:"descending"
| limit 1000
